Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺 好認真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的要做巧克力...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海同學打算送給誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單相思之類的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那傢伙很要好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不是人而是靈魂啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人竟然說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要天海同學的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼~?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然喜歡天海!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是個山田!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為天海同學一定會很細心地做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道一定會...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是巧克力?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是食慾啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哈... 給我巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我巧克力~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海做...巧克力?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:03:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海做巧克力...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種被超越的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有啦~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是連天海也有對象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是沒有沒有沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼東西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 你為什麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 因為今天紅豆特價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想用來做巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西不能加到巧克力裡面吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 巧克力這東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要做什麼樣的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不關我事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果你不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍為幫妳一下也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實她有一個我們不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的對象...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後為了他做巧克力的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會聽到天海的戀愛故事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣感覺好討厭啊~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 天海果然想做情人節巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買紅豆也很像天海同學的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得她應該是要做給鬼魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有可能是要做給喜歡的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也這麼想嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現階段也有可能是義理巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是給女孩子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要準備回禮喔 井上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真命天子要準備糖果喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要 要這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在場的人全部都是她的朋友吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是 朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼井上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己也承認是天海的朋友吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要有加紅豆的巧克力啦~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會加紅豆就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是喜歡和食的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海認識的人當中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會喜歡和食的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那傢伙的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要準備回禮嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會做好武士風範的傢伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士的風範...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗎 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正不是給他的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當完值日生後 肚子會餓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就算不是當值日生也會餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回禮...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海殿下為了在下...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 噹~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陰暗的老髮髻擺出沾沾自喜的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很煩躁~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下不過是在想要給天海殿下的回禮...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥? 回禮?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回什麼禮啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是海苔蛋啊 或是海苔蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒變的海苔蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下是要準備情人節之類的回禮...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情人節?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈... 不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了你做巧克力什麼的~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又懂什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算有也100%是義理巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是義理巧克力也不能輕易忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是武士的教養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥? 那是什麼 煩躁~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像妳一樣的死小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!? 真是令人火大!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個老髮髻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靈異現象~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是問一下她比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是對方是個怪人的話就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有什麼事嗎? 對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想直接一點會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日我先失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接一點... 什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要直接一點什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算在情人節之前告白之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道天海心儀的對象是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊! 妳們什麼時候出現的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是天海心儀的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像是怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海同學要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公園?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裡最近...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 現在的年輕人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力啊 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮浮躁躁的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼喝爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼喝爺爺?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近很出名喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上下學的人都很怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也被他吼過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是討厭情人節啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海想送巧克力的對象是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個爺爺嗎~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是自己做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力是食物不是嗜好品!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 老伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把拼命準備的東西送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了說出喜歡兩個字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何東西比這個奢侈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會冷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳... 妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 我們家的人這麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會 沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 之前跟您學的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆餡不要調得太甜會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年 因為太甜失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然弄清楚真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他很喜歡吃紅豆餡的糕餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐洋風味很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會用紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子打算送給誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在街上遊蕩 快回家!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真... 真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個爺爺真的是天海的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到她喜歡年紀大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定有什麼地方搞錯了~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個爺爺一定不是人啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山...山田同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 各位?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳 妳妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是認真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會有怨言的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對... 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去在意年齡的差別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 天海同學 嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得那個人不是人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(情人節當天)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收集巧克力中喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 謝謝!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在嗎? 有誰...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了這一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對男人來說最棒的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明顯是義理啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之食慾優先嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吉田竟然連一份巧克力也收不到?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這班女生 在害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有勇氣在情人節當天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把巧克力送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有必要覺得害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吉田 不論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會接受妳們的心意!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得剛才有股寒氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 先處理天海的事吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的打算送給他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海可能會激怒他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是竟然是那個呼喝爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 還在誤會啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響醬明明只是去見那個婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她打算送給誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊你 跟蹤狂?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在...在下只是擔心天海殿下的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一天海殿下發生什麼事的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 可是 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:15:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條路是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙打算去公園嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她應該已經沒必要去公園了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是去學巧克力的做法而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的意中人果然在公園...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是約好在公園見面?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去瞧瞧~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海同學終於要告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺好像不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 現在的年輕人真是懶散
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請停下他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 要我停下這個路人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是風嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要送給那個爺爺啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟上原殿下他們想的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼東西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳送什麼東西給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是婆婆教我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我做了多管閒事的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今年也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很想送給你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不在一年了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不可思議的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我習慣不浪費食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難吃 難吃! 很難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(謝謝妳)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海殿下 太善良了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於都追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會認同的! 不會認同的啊~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打...打起精神吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的心意一定 一定傳達的到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒... 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擺出那種表情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個... 果然跟鬼魂有關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會認同的~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幾時變成父親的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想吃天海同學的巧克力啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃好想吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是小屁孩嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是老爸還是小屁孩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天海同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也做了大家的份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們就用天海的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來辦情人節派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 井上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以說為什麼只對我說?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝招待...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
